Title: Verify Weather Forecast on Yahoo

Preconditions:
	•	A web browser is open
	•	The user is on the Yahoo homepage (https://www.yahoo.com)

Steps:
	1.	Open the Yahoo homepage
	2.	Locate the Weather block on the homepage
	3.	Click “See More” to open the full weather page
	4.	Choose any city from the available list or search for a city
	5.	View the weather forecast for any selected day
	6.	Validate that the forecast details (temperature, weather condition, humidity, etc.) are displayed correctly

Expected Result:
	•	The user is redirected to the detailed weather page
	•	The selected city’s weather forecast is displayed correctly
	•	The forecast includes key details such as temperature, weather condition, and additional data
